data.description:
VIEWS, VIEWS, VIEWS! Check out this UPDATED 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom ranch sitting at the end of a private drive overlooking the beautiful Ohio River. You will have the perfect amount of privacy on just over a half acre of land. Nice attached two-car garage. Move right in, this home is completely turn-key! 1100+ square feet on the main floor, and another 1100+ in the full basement- where you'll find your bonus room! Relax on the beautiful front patio or the oversized, covered deck out back. Entire roof was replaced and deck was built in 2021. New siding, bonus room built, and wood burner was installed 2022. New gas hot water tank, new furnace, HVAC, and entire house was rewired in 2020. Shed out back does have electric and is included with the sale. All appliances included with the sale, and if you like any furniture the seller is willing to negotiate.
Don't miss out! Call now for your private tour!
